<br>
If others want to do so, that's their perogative.<br>
<br>
If you're above level 45, and send me a tell while I'm not busy (which is uncommon) and are within target range, I'll cast it on you.  I never take anyone's money for this service.  The rest of the time I just say &quot;I'm busy&quot;, or &quot;I can't target you, sorry.&quot;<br>
<br>
Here's what I won't do:<br>
<br>
* Group anyone and cast it on myself.<br>
* Cast it on a full group without an enchanter.<br>
* Wait around to be found so I can cast it.<br>
I'm glad they are reported fixing the level exploit.  If you want KEI for your group, group an enchanter. I don't have time to wait around to buff people - other people apparently do, you should get your buffs from them.<br>
<br>
Bitter <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub136.ezboard.com/beqenchantersrealm.showUserPublicProfile?gid=astyd>astyd</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 121<br> <font color=#330000>(6/1/03 11:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=133.topic&index=45>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why I don't cast KEI</span><hr size=1> <br>
