<br>
However, there are two things that I wish would change.. donations, I think the expectation of lower levels - who by far are the most annoying KEI beggers from my experience - to get kei for free or 2pp is making it hard to be an enchanter non roleplay/anon.  So just charge 50pp .. enough with the donations.  This would cut down alot on the harassment I think.  The second thing is KEI begs in groups.. I get more tells for KEI and haste now playing in pop groups then I have ever in the past.  Its really frustrating to be playing and get constantly asked for buffs by random people.  It would be nice to see other enchanters start to say &quot;no&quot;to these requests while in groups.. maybe that would cut down on the problem a little.  Its not that I don't want to buff people and help them out, its just that I don't think players are understanding just how many tells enchanters are getting for these buffs. And casting a 1000k mana buff over and over really takes the fun out of playing in a group.<br>
<br>
Just a thought...<br>
